---
title: Smart Rustic Double Turkey Meatball Soup with Parmesan Toast Soldiers
description: There are few meals more comforting than a simple, heartwarming soup! We've filled this version with free-form DIY turkey meatballs packed with Parmesan and garlic, along with hearty veggies for the ultimate comfort food.

